data.meta_description: 6420 - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document contains contact details of various companies categorized by their industry. It lists the company name, contact person, and their mobile numbers. There are over 50 entries of companies from different sectors like art galleries, music stores, electronics stores, metal industries, cycle stores etc.
